e-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150428040920/http://santiagotimes.cl/gays-and-lesbians-in-chile-now-allowed-to-donate-blood/ |url-status=dead |archive-date=28 April 2015 |title=Gays and lesbians in Chile now allowed to donate blood |publisher=Santiago Times |date=25 April 2013 }}</ref><ref>[http://www.washingtonblade.com/2013/05/01/chile-drops-blood-donation-ban-for-gays/ Chile drops blood donation ban for gays.] Washington Blade</ref><ref>[http://www.movilh.cl/documentacion2013/Criterios-seleccion-donantes-Minsal.pdf Norma que regula el procedimiento de atenci\u00f3n de donantes de sangre] (in Spanish)</ref><ref>[http://www.hematologia.org/bases/arch1086.pdf Gu\u00eda Criterios Selecci\u00f3n Donantes de Sangre] (in Spanish)</ref><ref>[http://www.movilh.cl/historico-termina-prohicion-a-gays-lesbianas-y-bisexuales-para-donar-sangre-en-chile/ Hist\u00f3rico: Termina prohibici\u00f3n a gays, lesbianas y bisexuales para donar sangre en Chile] (in Spanish)</ref>\n|-\n| {{flag|China}}\n| {{No|Indefinite}}\n|\n| <ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.latitudenews.com/story/china-says-lesbians-may-donate-blood-but-not-gay-men/ |title=China says lesbians may donate blood, but not gay men \u2014 Latitude News |publisher=Latitudenews.com |accessdate=4 March 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140227081637/http://www.latitudenews.com/story/china-says-lesbians-may-donate-blood-but-not-gay-men/ |archive-date=27 February 2014 |url-status=dead  }}</ref>\n|-\n|{{flag|Colombia}}\n|data-sort-value=\"0\" {{Yes|No deferral}}\n|data-sort-value=\"0\" {{Yes|No deferral}}\n| <ref>{{cite web|language=es|url=http://www.elcolombiano.com/corte_constitucional_homosexualidad_no_es_impedimento_para_donar_sangre-CVEC_183706|title=Homosexualidad no es impedimento para donar sangre: Corte Constitucional|date=28 May 2012}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{flag|Costa Rica}}\n|data-sort-value=\"0\" {{Yes|No deferral}}\n|\n| <ref>{{Cite web|language=es|title=La igualdad del sistema costarricense enfocado en la percepci\u00f3n de la poblaci\u00f3n de mujeres y homosexuales|url=https://sagaldavison.wordpress.com/2015/07/27/la-igualdad-del-sistema-costarricense-enfocado-en-la-percepcion-de-la-poblacion-de-mujeres-y-homosexuales/|publisher=Mi tinta es el alma|first1=Sagal Davison|last1=Garc\u00eda|first2=Jason Hern\u00e1ndez|last2=Murillo|date=27 July 2015|access-date=7 February 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160313083024/https://sagaldavison.wordpress.com/2015/07/27/la-igualdad-del-sistema-costarricense-enfocado-en-la-percepcion-de-la-poblacion-de-mujeres-y-homosexuales/|archive-date=13 March 2016|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{flag|Croatia}}\n| {{No|Indefinite}}\n|\n| <ref>{{cite web | url = http://narodne-novine.nn.hr/clanci/sluzbeni/270049.html | publisher = [[Narodne novine]] | language = Croatian | title = Pravilnik o krvi i krvnim sastojcima |trans-title=Bylaw for blood and its contents | date = 16 December 1998 | quote = E`lanak 16. Trajno se iskljue`uju kao davatelji krvi: [...] osobe sa homoseksualnim pona\u0161anjem [...] | author = Ministry of Health (Croatia) | accessdate = 18 July 2011| author-link = Ministry of Health (Croatia) }}</ref>\n|-\n| {{flag|Czech Republic}}\n|data-sort-value=\"12\" {{Partial|1 year}}\n|data-sort-value=\"12\" {{Partial|1 year}}\n| <ref>{{cite web|language=cs|url=http://www.transfuznispolecnost.cz/get.php?cesta=%20doc/postupy/Dop_STL2007_03%20Zp%C5%AFsobilost%20d%C3%A1rce_V6_2012_04_19.doc%20&%20id=318|title=Doporu\u010den\u00ed Spole\u010dnosti pro transfuzn\u00ed l\u00e9ka\u0159stv\u00ed \u010cLS JEP \u010d. STL2007_03 ze dne 12. 4. 2007 verze 6 (2012_04)|publisher=Spole\u010dnost pro transfuzn\u00ed l\u00e9ka\u0159stv\u00ed \u010cLS JEP|page=8|format=DOC|accessdate=7 February 2013}}{{dead link|date=January 2018 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>\n|-\n| {{flag|Denmark}}\n|data-sort-value=\"4\" {{Partial|4 months}}<ref>[https://www.pinknews.co.uk/2020/01/21/denmark-gay-bisexual-men-donate-blood-abstinence-magnus-heunicke/amp/]</ref>\n|data-sort-value=\"4\" {{Partial|4 months}} \n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://bloddonor.dk/tapning-hvor-og-hvordan/karantaeneregler/liste-gaeldende-karantaeneregler/#seksuelkontakt|title=Seksuel kontakt|last=|first=|date=|website=|publisher=Bloddonorerne i Danmark|language=Danish|accessdate=9 September 2017}}</ref> In March 2020, [[Denmark]] implemented a policy that allows gay and bi men to donate blood after a 4 month deferral period.<ref>[https://www.pinknews.co.uk/2020/01/21/denmark-gay-bisexual-men-donate-blood-abstinence-magnus-heunicke/amp/]</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.washingtonblade.com/2018/08/24/denmark-to-revise-blood-donation-laws-in-2019/|title=Denmark to revise blood donation laws in 2019|date=24 August 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.pinknews.co.uk/2018/08/24/denmark-announces-gay-men-will-be-allowed-to-donate-blood-by-2019/|title=Denmark announces gay men will be able to donate blood by 2019|date=24 August 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{flag|Estonia}}\n|data-sort-value=\"12\" {{Partial|1 year}}\n|data-sort-value=\"12\" {{Partial|1 year}}\n| <ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.kliinikum.ee/verekeskus/doonorile |title=Vereloovutusest |publisher= Tartu \u00dclikooli Kliinikumi Verekeskus | language=Estonian |accessdate=22 November 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{flag|Finland}}\n|data-sort-value=\"12\" {{Partial|1 year}}\n|data-sort-value=\"12\" {{Partial|1 year}}\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bloodservice.fi/blood-donation/donate-blood/can-you-donate|title=Can you donate|publisher=Finnish Red Cross Blood Service|access-date=27 January 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{flag|France}}\n|data-sort-value=\"4\" {{Partial|4 months}} \n|\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.france24.com/en/20160711-france-gay-men-30-year-ban-donate-blood-lgbt-rights-equality|title=After 30-year ban, gay men in France allowed to donate blood |publisher=[[france24]] |date=11 July 2016 |accessdate=12 July 2016 }}</ref> Since 1 February 2020, [[France]] implemented a policy that allows gay and bi men to donate blood after a 4-month deferral period.<ref>{{cite web|title=Don du sang : la p\u00e9riode d'abstinence impos\u00e9e aux homosexuels r\u00e9duite d'un an \u00e0 4 mois |trans-title=Gift of blood: the period of abstinence imposed on homosexuals reduced from one year to 4 months|language=French|url=https://www.lexpress.fr/actualite/societe/sante/don-du-sang-la-periode-d-abstinence-imposee-aux-homosexuels-reduite-d-un-an-a-4-mois_2090073.html|publisher=[[L'Express]]|date=17 July 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{flag|Germany}}\n|data-sort-value=\"12\" {{Partial|1 year}}\n|\n| <ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.bundesaerztekammer.de/fileadmin/user_upload/downloads/pdf-Ordner/MuE/Richtlinie_Haemotherapie_2017.pdf |title=Richtlinie zur Gewinnung von Blut und Blutbestandteilen und zur Anwendung von Blutprodukten (Richtlinie H\u00e4motherapie) |trans-title=Guidelines for the collection of blood and blood components and the use of blood products (haemotherapy) |publisher=[[German Medical Association]] |year=2017 |accessdate=11 March 2019 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180413000008/http://www.bundesaerztekammer.de/fileadmin/user_upload/downloads/pdf-Ordner/MuE/Richtlinie_Haemotherapie_2017.pdf |archivedate=13 April 2018 }}</ref>\n|-\n| {{flag|Greece}}\n| {{No|Indefinite}}\n|\n|<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.economist.com/the-economist-explains/2018/04/16/why-some-countries-still-ban-gay-men-from-giving-blood|title=Why some countries still ban gay men from giving blood|date=16 April 2018|work=The Economist|access-date=31 October 2019|issn=0013-0613}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{flag|Hong Kong}}\n|data-sort-value=\"12\" {{Partial|1 year}}\n| \n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.gaystarnews.com/article/relaxed-rules-gay-men-donate-blood-hong-kong/#gs.4d5DNCU|title=Relaxed rules will allow gay men to donate blood in Hong Kong|date=14 September 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www5.ha.org.hk/rcbts/File/hh_enquiry.pdf |title=W