/2018/01/12/israel-has-lifted-its-ban-gay-and-bi-men-donating-blood|title=Israel has lifted its ban on gay and bi men donating blood}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.pinknews.co.uk/2018/01/11/israel-to-allow-gay-and-bisexual-men-to-donate-blood-regardless-of-when-they-last-had-sex/|title=Israel to allow sexually active gay and bi men to donate blood|date=11 January 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/.premium-pilot-program-will-allow-gay-israeli-men-to-donate-blood-1.5730127|title=Pilot Program in Israel Will Allow Gay Men to Donate Blood Without Abstaining From Sex|first=Ido|last=Efrati|date=25 September 2018|newspaper=Haaretz}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{flag|Italy}}\n|data-sort-value=\"0\" {{Yes|No deferral}}\n|data-sort-value=\"0\" {{Yes|No deferral}}\n| <ref name=\"Seed\"/><ref>{{Cite web|title = GAY E DONAZIONE DEL SANGUE|url = http://www.avisgiarre.it/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=537:gay-e-donazione-del-sangue&catid=9:articoli-informavis&Itemid=20|website = www.avisgiarre.it|access-date = 13 February 2016|last = Administrator|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160222072721/http://www.avisgiarre.it/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=537:gay-e-donazione-del-sangue&catid=9:articoli-informavis&Itemid=20|archive-date = 22 February 2016|url-status = dead|df = dmy-all}}</ref>High-risk sexual contact is banned irrespective of the partner's sex.<ref name=criteri_per_la_selezione_del_donatore>{{cite web|url=http://www.avis.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Allegato-III-Criteri-per-la-selezione-del-donatore.pdf|title=Criteri per la selezione del donatore|author=[[Ministero della Salute]]|page=39}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{flag|Japan}}\n|data-sort-value=\"6\" {{Partial|6 months}}\n|\n| <ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.jrc.or.jp/donation/about/refrain/detail_04/ |publisher=Japanese Red Cross Society |accessdate=14 June 2016|language=ja|title=\u30a8\u30a4\u30ba\u3001\u809d\u708e\u306a\u3069\u306e\u30a6\u30a4\u30eb\u30b9\u4fdd\