2|archive-date=6 October 2018|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{flag|Brazil}}\n|data-sort-value=\"12\" {{Partial|1 year}}\n|data-sort-value=\"12\" {{Partial|1 year}}\n| <ref>{{cite web|language=pt|url=http://pegasus.fmrp.usp.br/projeto/legislacao/portaria_2712_de_12_novembro_2013.pdf|title=Ordinance No. 2712 of November 12, 2013|accessdate=2 September 2015|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160117030201/http://pegasus.fmrp.usp.br/projeto/legislacao/portaria_2712_de_12_novembro_2013.pdf|archivedate=17 January 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{flag|Bulgaria}}\n|data-sort-value=\"0\" {{Yes|No deferral}}\n| \n| {{citation needed|date=July 2015}}\n|-\n| {{flag|Canada}}\n|data-sort-value=\"3\" {{Partial|3 months}}\n|data-sort-value=\"3\" {{Partial|3 months}} \n| Since 2019, a 3-month deferral period for gay and bi men donating blood was implemented throughout Canada.<ref name=\":0\" />\n|-\n| {{flag|Chile}}\n|data-sort-value=\"0\" {{Yes|No deferral}}\n|data-sort-value=\"0\" {{Yes|No deferral}}\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=http://santiagotimes.cl/gays-and-lesbians-in-chile-now-allowed-to-donate-blood/ |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150428040920/http://santiagotimes.cl/gays-and-lesbians-in-chile-now-allowed-to-donate-blood/ |url-status=dead |archive-date=28 April 2015 |title=Gays and lesbians in Chile now allowed to donate blood |publisher=Santiago Times |date=25 April 2013 }}</ref><ref>[http://www.washingtonblade.com/2013/05/01/chile-drops-blood-donation-ban-for-gays/ Chile drops blood donation ban for gays.] Washington Blade</ref><ref>[http://www.movilh.cl/documentacion2013/Criterios-seleccion-donantes-Minsal.pdf Norma que regula el procedimiento de atenci\u00f3n de donantes de sangre] (in Spanish)</ref><ref>[http://www.hematologia.org/bases/arch1086.pdf Gu\u00eda Criterios Selecci\u00f3n Donantes de Sangre] (in Spanish)</ref><ref>[http://www.movilh.cl/historico-termina-prohicion-a-gays-lesbianas-y-bisexuales-para-donar-sangre-en-chile/ Hist\u00f3rico: Termina prohibici\u00f3n a gays, lesbianas y bisexuales para donar sangre en Chile] (in Spanish)</ref>\n|-\n| {{flag|China}}\n| {{No|Indefinite}}\n|\n| <ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.latitudenews.com/story/china-says-lesbians-may-donate-blood-but-not-gay-men/ |title=China says lesbians may donate blood, but not gay men \u2014 Latitude News |publisher=Latitudenews.com |accessdate=4 March 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140227081637/http://www.latitudenews.com/story/china-says-lesbians-may-donate-blood-but-not-gay-men/ |archive-date=27 February 2014 |url-status=dead  }}</ref>\n|-\n|{{flag|Colombia}}\n|data-sort-value=\"0\" {{Yes|No deferral}}\n|data-sort-value=\"0\" {{Yes|No deferral}}\n| <ref>{{cite web|language=es|url=http://www.elcolombiano.com/corte_constitucional_homosexualidad_no_es_impedimento_para_donar_sangre-CVEC_183706|title=Homosexualidad no es impedimento para donar sangre: Corte Constitucional|date=28 May 2012}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{flag|Costa Rica}}\n|data-sort-value=\"0\" {{Yes|No deferral}}\n|\n| <ref>{{Cite web|language=es|title=La igualdad del sistema costarricense enfocado en la percepci\u00f3n de la poblaci\u00f3n de mujeres y homosexuales|url=https://sagaldavison.wordpress.com/2015/07/27/la-igualdad-del-sistema-costarricense-enfocado-en-la-percepcion-de-la-poblacion-de-mujeres-y-homosexuales/|publisher=Mi tinta es el alma|first1=Sagal Davison|last1=Garc\u00eda|first2=Jason Hern\u00e1ndez|last2=Murillo|date=27 July 2015|access-date=7 February 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160313083024/https://sagaldavison.wordpress.com/2015/07/27/la-igualdad-del-sistema-costarricense-enfocado-en-la-percepcion-de-la-poblacion-de-mujeres-y-homosexuales/|archive-date=13 March 2016|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{flag|Croatia}}\n| {{No|Indefinite}}\n|\n| <ref>{{cite web | url = http://narodne-novine.nn.hr/clanci/sluzbeni/270049.html | publisher = [[Narodne novine]] | language = Croatian | title = Pravilnik o krvi i krvnim sastojcima |trans-tit